README.me FILE

This is a simple poll and question voting site made
	following the django documentation.

Although there are other larger database systems to use,
	this project uses SQLite as it comes loaded with django.

This code can be run by

1. Create a virutal environment
2. Install django for python 3.x and make sure you are using python 3.x

When there is a need to make a change in your models

1. Alter models.py
2. python manage.py makemigrations
3. python manage.py migrate